I'll throw on my suit and meet you there.

00:44.561 --> 00:45.914
Awesome!

00:49.101 --> 00:52.591
Hmm, bodacious and tubular.

00:54.599 --> 00:57.584
Uh, excuse me,
moon doggie,

00:57.652 --> 00:58.685
