00:58.687 --> 00:59.446
Yeah?

00:59.457 --> 01:01.051
You don't surf, do you?

01:01.059 --> 01:02.569
Not a bit.

01:02.902 --> 01:06.609
Well how did Gidget get the idea
you are the big Kahuna?

01:06.627 --> 01:10.008
