02:01.781 --> 02:03.976
I'm not an idiot.

02:07.428 --> 02:08.699
Oopsie.

02:10.662 --> 02:12.333
Over here.

02:12.530 --> 02:13.948
Careful.

02:13.970 --> 02:15.575
What happened?

02:15.578 --> 02:16.881
