degenerate life flash before your eyes?

04:05.615 --> 04:07.093
I wish...

04:09.141 --> 04:11.470
No! No, no, it was...

04:12.143 --> 04:13.938
ah, you're not gonna believe me.

04:14.037 --> 04:15.387
