04:52.728 --> 04:54.996
He didn't have hands.

04:56.338 --> 05:01.139
It was just his head, kinda...
floating there, like...

05:01.151 --> 05:04.121
the great powerful Oz.

05:05.633 --> 05:08.135
Or one of the Pep Boys.

05:11.438 --> 05:13.044
Manny, Moe or Jack?

05:13.053 --> 05:14.541
Manny.

05:18.077 --> 05:19.390
And he spoke to me...

05:19.404 --> 05:23.624
Oh! You were able to hear him,
under water? How weird.

05:23.636 --> 05:26.123
Oh that's the part that bumps you?

05:26.736 --> 05:28.605
