have made up what he said to me.

05:36.498 --> 05:37.873
What did he say?

05:39.106 --> 05:42.482
Something that made my blood run cold.

05:42.500 --> 05:43.800
What?

05:45.564 --> 05:47.232
Never mind, I probably heard him wrong.

05:47.245 --> 05:49.855
-Charlie!
-Please don't make me say it!

05:49.856 --> 05:53.115
Come on Charlie, I am your brother.
Whatever it was,

05:53.141 --> 05:55.149
