06:27.689 --> 06:28.796
Sure.

06:28.797 --> 06:31.017
It's about what happens when you die.

06:31.061 --> 06:32.407
OK.

06:32.565 --> 06:34.332
Who gets your car?

06:37.251 --> 06:38.920
Go away.

06:39.818 --> 06:42.405
You're right,
it's not a good time to ask.

06:44.087 --> 06:45.565
So...

06:45.829 --> 06:47.171
