08:03.847 --> 08:04.876
How do you know?

08:04.880 --> 08:08.170
Did he talk to you?
No! He talked to me.

08:08.504 --> 08:10.438
Sure, rub my nose in it.

08:10.905 --> 08:12.105
How about this...

08:12.106 --> 08:15.966
When was the last time you called her,
just to see how she was doing?

08:16.001 --> 08:17.515
Uh...

08:17.546 --> 08:19.140
What's today, Sunday?

08:19.141 --> 08:21.114
Then... never.

08:21.759 --> 08:23.309
Why don't you start with that?

08:25.047 --> 08:27.298
OK, fine.

08:27.745 --> 08:29.444
Remember her number?

08:29.483 --> 08:31.415
I've got it on speed dial...

08:31.445 --> 08:33.815
666.

08:34.120 --> 08:35.734
Cute, uh?

08:38.283 --> 08:40.061
Hey Mom, it's Charlie.

08:40.691 --> 08:43.888
Nothing's the matter,
I just called to see how you're doing.

08:44.564 --> 08:49.271
No, I'm not drunk, I was just thinking
about you and thought I'd call.

08:50.029 --> 08:52.608
I swear to God,
I'm not drunk!

08:52.615 --> 08:56.311
Peter Piper picked a peck of
pickled peppers! Are you happy?

08:57.118 --> 09:00.133
So, what's going on?
I haven't talked to you in a while...

09:00.577 --> 09:03.696
