09:05.532 --> 09:08.835
OK, OK, OK.

09:08.926 --> 09:11.038
OK, excuse me?

09:11.513 --> 09:14.829
OK, OK, OK...

09:15.542 --> 09:16.766
So...

09:17.167 --> 09:19.007
Everything OK?

09:20.466 --> 09:22.624
I'm taking her to lunch tomorrow.

09:22.935 --> 09:24.762
Voluntarily?

09:25.012 --> 09:28.478
Wow, you must have really had
a spiritual experience out there...

09:28.490 --> 09:31.107
Let's face it Alan.
When Dad was alive,

09:31.140 --> 09:32.723
I was a rotten son.

09:32.732 --> 09:35.129
Oh, you sure were,
you were horrible.

09:35.145 --> 09:38.262
-Boy, I remember the time...
-The point is...

09:38.424 --> 09:41.177
Maybe I've got a chance
to make up for it now.

09:41.575 --> 09:45.517
He wants me to take care of mom,
then... that's what we're gonna do.

09:45.639 --> 09:48.592
Well, that's...
Wait a minute, did you say "we"?

09:49.358 --> 09:51.494
-I'm not going.
-Fine.

09:51.525 --> 09:55.887
Next time I see our father's floating head,
I'm gonna tell him you refused to help.

09:56.126 --> 09:59.721
I'm gonna tell him, I'm gonna tell him...
God, you're such a child...

09:59.747 --> 10:02.053
