16:53.239 --> 16:55.059
Can we just please change the subject?

16:55.060 --> 16:56.547
Although I must say,

16:56.565 --> 17:01.944
I prefer your mother to that post-pubescent
knucklehead your father replaced her with.

17:01.948 --> 17:03.458
OK, OK, that's it.

17:03.474 --> 17:05.041
What, I changed the subject!

17:05.042 --> 17:06.301
Come on Jake, we're going to the movies.

17:06.303 --> 17:07.344
On a school night?

17:07.345 --> 17:09.501
Why not, you're flunking anyway.

17:09.661 --> 17:11.587
Wait, wait,
you're just leaving me?

17:11.588 --> 17:13.755
You're taking care of Mom, remember?

17:13.768 --> 17:14.912
That's not fair.

17:14.915 --> 17:17.530
You got a complaint?
Take it to the floating head.

17:24.125 --> 17:25.579
So how is work?

17:25.924 --> 17:26.834
Fine.

17:26.839 --> 17:28.693
Are you seeing anybody special?

17:28.706 --> 17:29.799
Nope.

17:31.059 --> 17:33.856
Charlie, did you ever stop to think

17:33.878 --> 17:38.988
that our relationship is strained
because you won't let me, you won't share.

17:38.996 --> 17:40.932
You know why I won't share with you, Mom?

17:40.939 --> 17:43.363
Because anything I say
will be used against me.

17:43.364 --> 17:44.557
Oh please...

17:44.559 --> 17:47.687
I have to go to the bathroom,
maybe I have a prostate problem.

17:47.688 --> 17:51.708
I buy a new Mercedes,
you call it a Nazi phallic symbol.

17:51.974 --> 17:56.715
I'm seeing someone new, you ask if I'm
paying her by the hour, or per schtup!

17:57.313 --> 18:00.242
Charlie, when I say those things,
it's because I want to help you.

18:00.243 --> 18:04.108
You're my son, I want you
to be the best you can be.

18:04.109 --> 18:06.619
I appreciate that,
but you can stop worrying,

18:06.623 --> 18:10.499
I'm doing fine.
I am the best I can be.

18:10.836 --> 18:14.012
Oh darling, that just breaks my heart.

18:23.415 --> 18:25.600
Why would he do this to me?

18:25.685 --> 18:28.034
Take care of your mother...

18:28.406 --> 18:30.511
Not like she ever took care of him.

18:30.587 --> 18:35.179
She nagged him,
humiliated him, emasculated him.

18:35.554 --> 18:39.180
Maybe the reason he died so young
is because he wanted to.

18:39.876 --> 18:43.375
Charlie! My donut's soft again!

18:43.465 --> 18:45.113
Be right there!

18:46.541 --> 18:47.661
Why?

18:47.687 --> 18:50.149
Why do you want me
to take care of her?

18:50.150 --> 18:51.568
Charlie!

18:52.590 --> 18:54.302
I'm coming!

18:54.313 --> 18:57.846
Come on, talk to me!
Give me a sign!

18:57.847 --> 19:01.816
* Marry that cute girl down the beach. *

19:03.139 --> 19:04.035
Rose...

19:04.036 --> 19:06.600
* Yes, that's her name. *

19:08.771 --> 19:09.880
You know what,

19:09.881 --> 19:10.933
you can tell me in person,

19:10.950 --> 19:14.710
because I am this close
to sticking my tongue in a light socket.

19:15.683 --> 19:19.171
* Why don't you stick
your tongue in my mouth instead? *

19:19.723 --> 19:23.122
* I mean, Rose's mouth. *

19:32.030 --> 19:33.046
What are you watching?

19:33.048 --> 19:35.248
Some old gangster movie.

19:37.929 --> 19:39.078
Any good?

19:39.536 --> 19:40.658
Not really.

19:41.424 --> 19:43.074
It just gives me a warm feeling

19:43.078 --> 19:47.590
to know that all those young,
beautiful actors are now dead.

19:49.148 --> 19:51.138
"Dana knows too much."

19:51.194 --> 19:53.241
"You want I should
take care of her, boss?"

19:58.397 --> 20:00.724
"Yeah, take care of her."

20:00.751 --> 20:03.042
"But make it look like an accident."

20:05.471 --> 20:07.237
"Don't worry about a thing."

20:07.249 --> 20:09.039
"I'll take care of her."

20:10.522 --> 20:11.422
Sorry.

20:11.440 --> 20:13.311
I misunderstood.

20:16.052 --> 20:18.026
What's that, dear?

20:18.458 --> 20:19.728
Nothing.

20:34.550 --> 20:35.627
Hi.

20:36.541 --> 20:37.674
Hello.

20:38.550 --> 20:39.894
I don't know if you remember me,

20:39.896 --> 20:42.209
but I'm the one who pulled you out
of the ocean the other day.

20:42.227 --> 20:44.065
Oh, right! Right, right...

20:44.166 --> 20:44.715
Thanks!

20:44.723 --> 20:46.455
It's OK, it's my job.

20:46.636 --> 20:48.791
Well, I'm-I'm... glad you did it!

20:48.898 --> 20:51.855
Anyway, I was just checking in on you,
see how you're doing.

20:51.888 --> 20:52.997
I'm doing fine.

20:53.014 --> 20:54.100
Good...

20:55.298 --> 20:56.478
So...

20:56.655 --> 20:58.574
you want to walk down to the pier?

20:58.592 --> 21:00.786
Maybe grab a cup of coffee...

21:09.037 --> 21:11.293
Gee, I don't know...

21:11.294 --> 21:15.691
Charlie, it's time
to change my butt dressing.

21:18.125 --> 21:19.962
Eh, what the hell,
let's go.

